sourcesContent: class t{constructor(){this.current=this.detect();this.currentId=0}set(e){this.current!==e&&(this.currentId=0,this.current=e)}reset(){this.set(this.detect())}nextId(){return++this.currentId}get isServer(){return this.current==="server"}get isClient(){return this.current==="client"}detect(){return typeof window=="undefined"||typeof document=="undefined"?"server":"client"}}let n=new t;export{n as env};
